        "num": "01",
        "body": "Catch the moment before you react — name what's actually happening.",
        "bg": "#0F7A6E",
        "accent": "#FFD166"
      },
      {
        "label": "Name",
        "num": "02",
        "body": "Put it in one plain sentence. Vague feelings shrink once they're words.",
        "bg": "#E0A100",
        "accent": "#0F1E1C"
      },
      {
        "label": "Navigate",
        "num": "03",
        "body": "Pick the smallest next action. Momentum beats a perfect plan.",
        "bg": "#E6452F",
        "accent": "#FFF6E9"
      }
